high_descs: walk forwards to the kitchen counter up ahead
grab the potato off of the kitchen counter
turn left to face the microwave
place the potato inside of the microwave, turn it on, cook it, then take it back out
turn left and walk over to the front of the refrigerator on your right
place the potato inside of the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved potato inside of the refrigerator

high_descs: Move forward then head to the counter beside the toaster
Pick up the potato beside the toaster at the counter
Open the microwave then heat the potato wait few seconds take it out then close the microwave
Turn left then move few steps face the fridge
Open the fridge and put in the potato
anns.task_desc: Put heated potato in the fridge

high_descs: Pick up potato from counter, to the left of toaster.
Open microwave door.  Place potato in microwave, close door.  Wait three seconds.  Open microwave, remove potato, close door.
Turn left to go to refrigerator.  Turn right to face refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, put potato on second shelf down under lettuce, close refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Pick up potato, warm in microwave, put in refrigerator.
